wo years since it found its way into the world. Nonetheless, <span>Callahan</span> will return with a new LP later this year entitled Dream River. Released through Drag City on September 17th, Dream River is said to be \"easily the most sensual and soulful of <span>Callahan</span>\'s career.\" There you go. Check out the tracklisting below. Dream River 01 The Sing 02 Javelin Unlanding 03 Small Plane 04 Spring 05 Ride My Arrow 06 Summer Painter 07','http://beatsperminute.com/news/bill-callahan-announces-new-album-dream-river/','2013-06-19T00:00:00','2013-06-19T11:35:28');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('cc1367dd77ff466c7b59a145afd7f780','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan regressa ao estúdio','inspirou títulos de Laura Marling, vai voltar aos discos. O próximo título será Dream River, num álbum com selo da Drag City que chega às lojas a 17 de Setembro. Este terá apenas oito músicas mas é descrito pela editora como \"facilmente o álbum mais sensual e cheio de alma da carreira de <span>Callahan</span>\", o que eleva ainda mais as expectativas dos fãs que se deleitaram com Apocalypse (2011).Dream River foi gravado numa cidade com o peculiar nome de Cacophony, no Texas, e aborda temáticas como \"voar para casa num pequeno avião, beber com os ocupantes de um hotel como companhia, pintar barcos para o Verão, ou','http://www.punch.pt/2013/06/18/bill-callahan-regressa-ao-estudio/','2013-06-19T00:00:00','2013-06-18T23:57:45');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('60866143a50f3610a2936d07eb6a5fce','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan anuncia nuevo disco, Dream River','el lanzamiento de su nuevo disco de estudio, Dream River, que saldrá a la venta el 17 de septiembre a través de Drag City. La continuación del álbum Apocalypse del 2011 se grabó el año pasado en Cacophony, Texas, y es descrito por Drag City como \"sin duda, el más sensual y conmovedor en la carrera de <span>Callahan</span>\". El trabajo de ocho canciones habla sobre diferentes temas, como el \"volar a casa en un pequeño avión, pintar los barcos para el verano, o volar hacia el mar a lo largo de la ruta del río de ensueño sin la ayuda de alguna embarcación\", entre otras cosas. Tracklist Dream River: 01. The Sing 02. Javelin Unlanding','http://radioalterno.com/2013/06/bill-callahan-anuncia-nuevo-disco-dream-river/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bill-callahan-anuncia-nuevo-disco-dream-river','2013-06-18T00:00:00','2013-06-18T16:26:39');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('ff0c8b2e7c141ed5191e5f81639e5474','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','whats good','do that.* The Molybden album \"Songs from Lincoln\" is pretty amazingly somber and beautiful AND features a killer cover of Rosanne Cash\'s Seven Year Ache.* Pitchfork announced this morning that Bill Callahan recorded his next Drag City release at Cacophony studios and that it\'ll come out 9/17. The title once again uses frequent <span>Callahan</span> vocabulary words \"dream\" and \"river.\"* So there you have it, that\'s about all there is to know. Oh, there are some festivals coming up I think. You should go to the Fun Fun Fun Fest one. All of your favorite acts and acts you thought you\'d never get to see live will be','http://partyends.com/blog/?p=5440','2013-06-19T00:00:00','2013-06-18T14:12:20');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('2ca45cf6c1263fd3b462a6223253be8d','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan Details New Album: ‘Dream River’','for today\'s press shot and Drag City describing the album as \"sensual and soulful,\" it looks like Bill Callahan has an uncharacteristically upbeat set on the way. Even its title, Dream River, suggests he\'s risen from 2011′s Apocalypse in good spirits. Put to tape at Cacophony Recorders in <span>Callahan</span>\'s adopted homebase of Austin, Texas, the 8-track LP arrives on September 17th. Check out the titles below:Dream River Tracklist 01. \"The Sing\" 02. \"Javelin Unlanding\" 03. \"Small Plane\" 04. \"Spring\" 05. \"Ride My Arrow\" 06. \"Summer Painter\" 07. \"Seagull\" 08. \"Winter Road\" Bill Callahan Details New Album:','http://www.twentyfourbit.com/2013/06/bill-callahan-dream-river/','2013-06-19T00:00:00','2013-06-18T14:05:40');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('df10caacb566c86ff428124b18a65a60','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Il nuovo disco di Callahan','Bill Callahan annucia \"Dream River\" nuovo LP successore dell`ottimo \"Apocalypse\". Release date 17 settembre, etichetta Drag City. Il nuovo disco di <span>Callahan</span> pubblicato su Indie For BUNNIES Il nuovo disco di <span>Callahan</span>','http://www.indieforbunnies.com/2013/06/18/il-nuovo-disco-di-callahan/','2013-06-19T00:00:00','2013-06-18T13:53:56');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('65efb8b53d25f11670a0b4aaed8f015b','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan Dream River Details','Bill Callahan has been in the game a long, long time; he released his first album as Smog 23 years ago. But until this moment, I don\'t think I\'ve ever seen a press photo of him smiling. Take that as an indication, then, that <span>Callahan</span>\'s next album won\'t showcase the dark, mordant wit that made him indie-famous -- or maybe that that wit will take different forms. In a few months, <span>Callahan</span> will release Dream River, his follow-up to 2011′s much-loved Apocalypse. <span>Callahan</span> recorded the album earlier this year in the amazingly named town of Cacophony, Texas, and a press release calls its eight songs \"easily the most sensual and soulful of <span>Callahan</span>\'s career.\" Check the tracklist below. Read More... Original Website: Stereogum Bill Callahan Dream River Details','http://www.groove2u.net/bill-callahan-dream-river-details/','2013-06-18T00:00:00','2013-06-18T13:20:36');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('56d3d34d81b00efc6a5cd6bcb0a8ebf3','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan Dream River Details','Bill Callahan has been in the game a long, long time; he released his first album as Smog 23 years ago. But until this moment, I don\'t think I\'ve ever seen a press photo of him smiling. Take that as an indication, then, that <span>Callahan</span>\'s next album won\'t showcase the dark, mordant wit that made him indie-famous -- or maybe that that wit will take different forms. In a few months, <span>Callahan</span> will release Dream River, his follow-up to 2011′s much-loved Apocalypse. <span>Callahan</span> recorded the album earlier this year in the amazingly named town of Cacophony, Texas, and a press release calls its eight songs \"easily the most sensual and soulful of <span>Callahan</span>\'s career.\" Check the tracklist below. Read More... Bill Callahan Dream River Details','http://stereogum.feedsportal.com/c/34853/f/643485/s/2d7370d4/l/0L0Sstereogum0N0C13845810Cbill0Ecallahan0Edream0Eriver0Edetails0Cnews0C/story01.htm','2013-06-19T00:00:00','2013-06-18T13:20:36');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('8a554683387552b6f2c37e0b4cb37c07','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan: nieuw album Dream River in september','elkaar in rap tempo op. Volgende plaat om alvast naar uit te kijken: een nieuwe van songschrijver Bill Callahan. Hij volgt zijn uitstekende laatste plaat Apocalypse op met Dream River, uit op 17 september via Drag City. Volgens het begeleidend schrijven bij de plaat \"easily the most sensual and soulful of <span>Callahan</span>\'s career\". Dat belooft een hoop goeds weer, hopelijk laat een eerste voorbode van de plaat niet lang op zich wachten. Dream River tracklist: 01. The Sing 02. Javelin Unlanding 03. Small Plane 04. Spring 05. Ride My Arrow 06. Summer Painter 07. Seagull 08. Winter RoadBill <span>Callahan</span> - Tiny Desk','http://kickingthehabit.nl/2013-06-18/bill-callahan-nieuw-album-dream-river-in-september','2013-06-18T00:00:00','2013-06-18T13:20:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('0a7f6a2752400eb60a3b53f26e17a79d','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','And Bands: Conor Oberst and the Mystic Valley Band','Photo courtesy of Katherine L. EhleConor Oberst and the Mystic Valley Band: Danny <span>Callahan</span> [purchase the studio version] It struck me that I\'ve been writing for this blog for about a year and a half without posting about one of my favorite bands, Wilco. Not on this blog, at least. I\'ve seen Wilco perform a few times, and their shows are almost always memorable. My favorite one, however, was an outdoor show in 2009 at the minor league baseball stadium in Wappinger\'s Falls, New York (home of the Hudson Valley Renegades). It was a beautiful summer night, I was there with my son, we stood close enough to ... impressed and even converted most (if clearly not all) of the audience, some of whom sadly had no interest in appreciating the quality of the performance and just wanted to get on to the headliner. They set a high bar that night, and Wilco actually surpassed them, which is no shame. \"Danny <span>Callahan</span>,\" from Oberst\'s self-titled album, is one of my son\'s favorites, and for good reason. A great, almost bouncy, melody is coupled with literate and uplifting lyrics, but about a very serious subject, the death of a young cancer patient, failed by \"Western medicine\". That night, my son and I stood in front','http://sixsongs.blogspot.com/2013/06/and-bands-conor-oberst-and-mystic.html','2013-06-11T00:00:00','2013-06-10T18:07:18');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('256beeb7aa81c3787227b3d4184a3fca','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Preview The Life and Times of William Callahan, a Photo Essay by Chris Taylor','Recently, Canadian photographer Chris Taylor went to Texas for a month with the mission of photographing Bill Callahan every other day for a month. He captured the heavy-hearted, baritone-voiced singer in and around his Austin ... read more » Preview The Life and Times of William <span>Callahan</span>, a Photo Essay by Chris Taylor','http://www.thefader.com/2013/06/07/preview-the-life-and-times-of-william-callahan-a-photo-essay-by-chris-taylor/','2013-06-08T00:00:00','2013-06-07T17:07:12');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('c05090ac14a19256b794009f7b130453','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Diablo 3 Releases on September 3rd for Xbox 360 and PlayStation 3','at Sony\'s PlayStation 4 reveal. Today Blizzard has confirmed the game will be out on Microsoft\'s Xbox 360 along with the PlayStation 3 version on September 3rd. Diablo 3\'s console release features four player local co-op or four player online co-op. The game also supports combo co-op so you can combine local and online players. Blizzard has also carefully redesigned the interface to account for multiple players and the controller. Our own Tally <span>Callahan</span> went hands on with it at PAX East and came away mightily impressed. Read More Diablo 3 Releases on September 3rd for Xbox 360 and PlayStation 3','http://www.co-optimus.com/article/10296/diablo-3-releases-on-september-3rd-for-xbox-360-and-playstation-3.html','2013-06-06T00:00:00','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('fc87a4b8066a3da2a73dc48b6600c20d','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Giants&#8217; Safety Antrel Rolle &#8216;Not Eager&#8217; to See RGIII Again','team\'s owner Jerry Jones, who\'s notorious for meddling with/alienating his coaching staff, as he did after the Redskins abruptly ended Dallas\'s season with a 28-18 Week 17 victory, by hiring Bill Callahan as offensive coordinator. Jones has since progressed this offseason storyline, by officially announcing Tuesday that <span>Callahan</span> will run the offense in 2013, and not head coach Jason Garrett. Back to the Redskins. Rolle was asked about RGIII, who\'s light-years ahead of schedule in the rehab of his surgically repaired knee. \"I\'m not so eager to see this guy,\" Rolle said. His trepidation to','http://washington.cbslocal.com/2013/06/04/giants-safety-antrel-rolle-not-eager-to-see-rgiii-again/','2013-06-04T00:00:00','2013-06-04T19:42:54');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('fbd5dc86b58b5162f1554e84c02f58a9','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Mozilla coder: Chrome violates Google\'s own Blink principles','Programmer Robert O\'<span>Callahan</span> objects that Google\'s Native Client technology contradicts laudable Web standards principles the Net giant laid out for Blink, its new browser engine project. [Read more] Mozilla coder: Chrome violates Google\'s own Blink principles','http://news.cnet.com/8301-1023_3-57587156-93/mozilla-coder-chrome-violates-googles-own-blink-principles/?part=rss&subj=news&tag=title','2013-05-31T00:00:00','2013-05-31T21:03:45');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('9dac5234c3b49c01755438ca54a91157','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan announces release of new album, Dream River','Recorded at the Cacophony Recorders studio in Austin, Texas - which has also been used by M Ward, My Morning Jacket, White Denim and Explosions In The Sky - the eight-track album follows 2011\'s Apocalypse, 2009\'s Sometimes I Wish We Were An Eagle and 2007\'s Woke On A Whaleheart. <span>Callahan</span> will be supporting the record\'s release with a full tour this autumn, details of which will be announced shortly. The album will come out on his long-term label, Drag City. The Dream River tracklisting is: \'The Sing\' \'Javelin Unlanding\' \'Small Plane\' \'Spring\' \'Ride My Arrow\' \'Summer Painter\' \'Seagull\' \'Winter Road\'','http://www.uncut.co.uk/bill-callahan/bill-callahan-announces-release-of-new-album-dream-river-news','2013-06-19T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('a62d4debacc5bda129206742d1c1feeb','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','LOOK: Bill Callahan Announces New Album \"Dream River,\" Slated for September Release','Callahan announced that his new album Dream River, the follow-up to 2011\'s critical darling Apocalypse, is set for a September 17th release via Drag City. The album was recorded at Cacophony, Texas, earlier this year, and boasts eight tracks that Drag City assures are \"easily the most sensual and soulful of <span>Callahan</span>\'s career.\" Subject matter for the songs off Dream River includes flying home in a small plane and painting boats for the summer. Though <span>Callahan</span> is an incredibly prolific artist, each of his releases is exceptional, and it doesn\'t make us any less excited for Dream River. Check out the tracklist','http://filtermagazine.com/index.php/news/entry/look_bill_callahan_announces_new_album_dream_river_slated_for_september_rel','2013-06-18T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('2888cef907cbaa6632bd6b4e7d2991e4','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan Announces New LP, Dream River','Photo by Hanly Banks Bill Callahan has announced the follow-up to his excellent 2011 album Apocalypse. Dream River is out September 17 via Drag City. The album was recorded at Cacophony, TX earlier this year. A press release calls it \"easily the most sensual and soulful of <span>Callahan</span>\'s career\"; he\'s also planning an extensive tour this fall. Check out the tracklist below. Dream River: 01 The Sing 02 Javelin Unlanding 03 Small Plane 04 Spring 05 Ride My Arrow 06 Summer Painter 07 Seagull 08 Winter Road Check out a Pitchfork.tv video of <span>Callahan</span> performing the Smog classic \"Cold Blooded Old Times\" below.','http://pitchfork.com/news/51209-bill-callahan-announces-new-lp-dream-river/','2013-06-18T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('93f7a814549331446f2cdc653d3001e9','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan announces release of new album \'Dream River\'','recorded as Smog, will put out his fourth LP under his own name on September 16. Recorded at the Cacophony Recorders studio in Austin, Texas - which has also been used by M Ward, My Morning Jacket, White Denim and Explosions In The Sky - the eight track album follows 2011\'s \'Apocalypse\', 2009\'s \'Sometimes I Wish We Were an Eagle\' and 2007\'s \'Woke on a Whaleheart\'. <span>Callahan</span> will be supporting the record\'s release with a full tour this autumn, details of which will be announced shortly. The album will come out on his long-term label, Drag City. Bill Callahan announces release of new album \'Dream River\'','http://www.nme.com/news/bill-callahan/70924','2013-06-18T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('c9132a59a49c4a181d46dc756182bbc9','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan Dream River Details','Bill Callahan has been in the game a long, long time; he released his first album as Smog 23 years ago. But until this moment, I don\'t think I\'ve ever seen a press photo of him smiling. Take that as an indication, then, that <span>Callahan</span>\'s next album won\'t showcase the dark, mordant wit that made him indie-famous -- or maybe that that wit will take different forms. In a few months, <span>Callahan</span> will release Dream River, his follow-up to 2011′s much-loved Apocalypse. <span>Callahan</span> recorded the album earlier this year in the amazingly named town of Cacophony, Texas, and a press release calls its eight songs \"easily the most sensual and soulful of <span>Callahan</span>\'s career.\" Check the tracklist below. 01 \"The Sing\" 02 \"Javelin Unlanding\" 03 \"Small Plane\" 04 \"Spring\" 05 \"Ride My Arrow\" 06 \"Summer Painter\" 07 \"Seagull\" 08 \"Winter Road\" Dream River is out 9/17 on Drag City. Bill Callahan Dream River Details','http://www.stereogum.com/1384581/bill-callahan-dream-river-details/news/','2013-06-18T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('05f691a6c07fe09dcce2de8917377cd8','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan Announces New Album','up with the documentary Apocalypse: A Bill Callahan Tour Film. Now, it\'s safe to say Bill\'s apocalypse is over, as he\'s announced a new album with less of an end-times theme. The new record is called Dream River, and features eight brand new songs from the artist. A press release describes it as \"easily the most sensual and soulful of <span>Callahan</span>\'s career.\" Drag City will release the album on September 17. Check out the tracklisting below. Dream River: 1. The Sing 2. Javelin Unlanding 3. Small Plane 4. Spring 5. Ride My Arrow 6. Summer Painter 7. Seagull 8. Winter Road Bill Callahan Announces New Album','http://exclaim.ca/News/bill_callahan_announces_new_album_2','2013-06-18T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('224b761ad1dd153c3af0ab1837c793f3','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan Sets &#039;Sensual, Soulful&#039; September LP &#039;Dream River&#039;','Smog, on September 17 via longtime home Drag City. Dream River was recorded earlier this year at Cacophony, Texas -- presumably the Austin studio and not a miraculously named town unsearchable via Google Maps -- and contains eight tracks billed by the label as \"easily the most sensual and soulful of <span>Callahan</span>\'s career.\" An announcement suggests the song\'s subjects may include \"flying home in a small plane, drinking with the sleeping inhabitants of a hotel for company, painting boats for the summer, or flying towards the sea along the path of the dream river without the aid of any craft.\" While SPIN\'s Apocalypse reviewer Mike Powell noted it\'s easy to mistakenly hear <span>Callahan</span>\'s songs as sad, the new press photo above showcases a disarming grin. <span>Callahan</span> plans to keep busy with a fall tour, though dates have not been announced yet. Dream River track list: 1. \"The Sing\" 2. \"Javelin Unlanding\" 3. \"Small Plane\" 4. \"Spring \" 5. \"Ride My Arrow\" 6. \"Summer Painter\" 7. \"Seagull\" 8. \"Winter Road\" Bill Callahan Sets &#039;Sensual, Soulful&#039; September LP &#039;Dream River&#039;','http://www.spin.com/articles/bill-callahan-dream-river-september-album/','2013-06-18T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('f503a5389f4ad5d2b573830add2eb33d','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Schwagstock Founder Jimmy Tebeau Heads to Federal Prison','to charge him under a broader statute that makes it a crime to knowingly allow drug sales on one\'s property. The federal government then invoked asset forfeiture laws to confiscate Camp Zoe. According to the Riverfront Times (who have published an extensive report on the subject), U.S. Attorney Richard <span>Callahan</span> stated that \"We didn\'t view this a music-festival prosecution...we viewed it as somebody who was using a festival site to promote illegal drug sales and profit off of that. We thought there was a difference between a music festival with incidental drug use and a drug festival with incidental','http://www.jambands.com/news/2013/06/13/schwagstock-founder-jimmy-tebeau-heads-to-federal-prison','2013-06-13T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('9d786e8501bc84e11c409fa4788e303c','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','See Laura Marling&#039;s &#039;Master Hunter,&#039; a Harrowing Dance Duet','Laura Marling\'s \"Master Hunter\" came crashing out of the gate like an amped up combination of Bill Callahan\'s baritone blues and Fiona Apple\'s frenetic folk. The former comparison seems almost too fitting considering the title of her forthcoming album, Once I Was an Eagle, sounds like a retort to <span>Callahan</span>\'s 2009 masterpiece Sometimes I Wish We Were an Eagle. We\'ve also heard the gentler, Dylanesque \"Where Can I Go?\" from the May 28 set (coming via Ribbon Music), but there\'s something about \"Master Hunter\" that\'s impossible to ignore. That forceful energy is captured and somewhat explained by the','http://www.spin.com/articles/laura-marling-master-hunter-video-ballet-eagle/','2013-05-07T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('e1107a46e429fb608be324ef5c04c06b','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Kirin J Callahan - \"Embracism\" Video (NSFW)','In his video for \"Embracism,\" Kirin J <span>Callahan</span> wakes up naked, shows off copious buttcheek and a few homemade-looking tattoos, lets out a mighty groan, and begins to grunt out his lurching, Suicide-addled post-industrial grind. The clip starts out as a sexed-up leer and gradually transforms into a symphony of glitches and creeped-out gestures. Cara Stricker got extremely up close and personal with <span>Callahan</span> to film it. Watch it and download the song below. Kirin J Callinan - \"Embracism\"Download <span>Callahan</span>\'s album Embracism is out 7/2 on Siberia/Terrible. Kirin J <span>Callahan</span> - \"Embracism\" Video','http://stereogum.com/1343141/kirin-j-callahan-embracism-video-nsfw/video/','2013-05-07T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('1e1c94af8c851bee1ae1f06d45583758','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Destroyer Albums From Worst To Best','album I was working on. Rubies was so great it actually made me mad at Dan Bejar. I was totally jealous. This has really only happened one other time -- when I heard Bill Callahan\'s A River Ain\'t Too Much To Love while making a previous album. As such, I put Bejar alongside <span>Callahan</span> (and Vic Chesnutt) as one of the greatest that ever was. You hear that kind of thing a lot about Bejar. A sensational songsmith and quite possibly the greatest lyricist of his generation, throughout his seventeen-year recording career as Destroyer he has been an ever evolving bastion of brilliance, beginning strong with his dedicatedly','http://stereogum.com/1305612/destroyer-albums-from-worst-to-best/top-stories/lead-story/','2013-04-12T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('ea5db472ec4d47728e4767938ef816a5','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','On \"All Your Women Things,\" Smog schools listeners on love, loss, and breasts','of blends together (in my mind, at least) to form this serene but beautiful clump of melancholy tracks. That\'s how, even though I\'ve been listening to 1997\'s Red Apple Falls pretty much exclusively lately, I\'ve found myself obsessed once again with \"All Your Women Things\" off 1996\'s The Doctor Came At Dawn. <span>Callahan</span>\'s ode to lingerie, \"All Your Women Things\" is a nearly 7-minute master class on how to write a song about love, loss, and breasts. <span>Callahan</span> rues, in that unmistakable baritone, that he ignored a woman he\'s lost either because of a breakup or a death, saying \"Well it\'s been seven years / ... fact that he ignored \"your left breast / your right breast\" and marvels at \"All your bridges and bras / Your cotton and gauze / All your buckles and straps / Releases and traps.\" It would be incredibly romantic if it weren\'t just unbelievably heartbreaking. (It\'s also a little bit creepy, as <span>Callahan</span> songs are wont to be. In the bridge, he says he\'s gathered all the woman\'s leftover lingerie and made \"a spread-eagle dolly.\") Gut wrenching, eerie, or swoon-worthy, though, \"All Your Women Things\" is pretty much perfect. It\'s one of <span>Callahan</span>\'s best songs, and definitely one of my all-time favorites by any','http://www.avclub.com/articles/on-all-your-women-things-smog-schools-listeners-on,96123/','2013-04-08T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('817b04cf17eae6b051fd35655eb258a8','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan Announces Summer Tour','In his first tour since summer 2011, singer-songwriter Bill Callahan (of Smog fame) will be hitting several U.S. cities early this summer, beginning with a performance at Proud Larry\'s in Oxford, Miss. on April 30. According to the press release announcing the tour, <span>Callahan</span> will be road-testing songs for his follow-up album to 2011\'s warmly received Apocalypse. Listed below are the confirmed tour dates. Bill Callahan\'s Tour Dates: April 30 - Oxford, Miss. @ Proud Larry\'s May 1 - Nashville, Tenn. @ Exit/In 2 - Louisville, Ky. @ Headliners 3 - Nelsonville, Ohio. @ Stuart\'s Opera House 4 - Oberlin,','http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2013/03/bill-callahan-announces-summer-tour.html','2013-03-14T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('39cb0e55be7c23e6d83f657170c6e7f0','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan announces dates for intimate, coastless spring tour','Callahan has announced the dates for a 10-city tour beginning Apr. 30 in Oxford, Mississippi. And in news likely to disappoint any fans foolish enough to be seduced by the coasts\' empty charm, though his stops will span from the mighty Midwest to the Great Plains, <span>Callahan</span> won\'t be going anywhere near an ocean. This will be his first tour since summer 2011, when he went on the road to promote his album Apocalypse. Dates are below. [via Pitchfork] Apr. 30--Proud Larry\'s--Oxford, Mississippi May 1--Exit/In--Nashville, Tennessee May 2--Headliners--Louisville, Kentucky May 3--Stuart\'s Opera House--Nelsonville,','http://www.avclub.com/articles/bill-callahan-announces-dates-for-intimate-coastle,93694/','2013-03-13T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('d23e1bdd94416ba8ecf54534b2dfe5e6','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Bill Callahan Announces Spring Tour','For the first time since summer 2011, Bill Callahan is hitting the road. According to a press release, it\'s likely that <span>Callahan</span> will be debuting some new songs he\'s been working on since his excellent 2011 record Apocalypse. Dates below. 04-30 Oxford, MS - Proud Larry\'s 05-01 Nashville, TN - Exit/In 05-02 Louisville, KY - Headliners 05-03 Nelsonville, OH - Stuart\'s Opera House 05-04 Oberlin, OH - Dionysus Club (the \'Sco) 05-07 Columbia, MO - Mojo\'s 05-08 Kansas City, MO - Record Bar 05-09 Norman, OK - The Opolis 05-10 Dallas, TX - The Prophet Bar 05-11 Austin, TX - Central Presbyterian Church Check out a Pitchfork.tv video of <span>Callahan</span> performing the Smog classic \"Cold Blooded Old Times\" below. Bill Callahan Announces Spring Tour','http://pitchfork.com/news/49894-bill-callahan-announces-spring-tour/','2013-03-13T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBiographies (ENBiographies.site,ENBiographies.artist_id,ENBiographies.desc,ENBiographies.truncated,ENBiographies.url,ENBiographies.licence_attribution,ENBiographies.licence_attribution_url,ENBiographies.licence_type,ENBiographies.licence_url,ENBiographies.licence_version) VALUES ('myspace','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','THE CALLAHANBAND IS A ROWDY COUNTRY BAND WITH A HARD ...',true,'http://www.myspace.com/thecallahanband','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBiographies (ENBiographies.site,ENBiographies.artist_id,ENBiographies.desc,ENBiographies.truncated,ENBiographies.url,ENBiographies.licence_attribution,ENBiographies.licence_attribution_url,ENBiographies.licence_type,ENBiographies.licence_url,ENBiographies.licence_version) VALUES ('last.fm','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','There are three bands that go by the name Callahan.  (1)A metal band from Vancouver. http://www.myspace.com/callahanband  (2)A pop-punk band from Springfield,Ohio. Myspace: myspace.com/thislove Now with new members and re-named This Love  (3)An instrumental pop band from Perú.  The official site is www.callahan.sugarpop.org',0,'http://www.last.fm/music/callahan/+wiki','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBiographies (ENBiographies.site,ENBiographies.artist_id,ENBiographies.desc,ENBiographies.truncated,ENBiographies.url,ENBiographies.licence_attribution,ENBiographies.licence_attribution_url,ENBiographies.licence_type,ENBiographies.licence_url,ENBiographies.licence_version) VALUES ('facebook','AR0DCWD11A348F0D16','Hailing from Springfield, Ohio, Callahan has quickly caught the attention ...',true,'http://graph.facebook.com/29762575783','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENTerms (ENTerms.name,ENTerms.artist_id,ENTerms.frequency,ENTerms.weight) VALUES ('co