 I should elaborate more in the coming days/weeks once I hear it with headphones. But initially, the prog-side is still apparent on a few tracks as the review below refers to. The opening suite piece \"The Humors of Tuaimgreine/RakishPadddy/<span>The Callahan</span> Stomp\" \"Redemption Song\" and the closer \"Dominion of the Sword.\" One thing I noticed in the write-up below, how it says this is their 7th studio album, but I believe that is off by 1 or 2. Not only due to John Wright mentioning this being their 9th album last night at the cd','http://allmediareviews.blogspot.com/2011/11/lehto-wright-dominion-of-sword-2012.html','2012-02-01T00:00:00','2012-01-21T23:27:36');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('e7da947150592aacee697604272a96e4','ARNKYES1187FB45230','Support local music at Callahan\'s in Azusa','Here is <span>the Callahan</span>\'s entertainment schedule for May: Fri 6 - Shades of LA Sat 7 ~ Kool <span>Breeze</span> Fri 13 ~ Liverz & Lungz Sat 14 ~ Sound Bytes fri 20 ~ Impulse Band Sat 21 ~ David Leon Fri 27 ~ Flirt Sat 28 ~ Plus Size Models Callahan\'s Fine Foods and Spirits 200 S. Irwindale Ave Azusa, CA 626-334-5532 ... Support local music at Callahan\'s in Azusa','http://mickieszoo.blogspot.com/2011/04/support-local-music-at-callahans-in.html','2011-05-12T00:00:00','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBiographies (ENBiographies.site,ENBiographies.artist_id,ENBiographies.desc,ENBiographies.truncated,ENBiographies.url,ENBiographies.licence_attribution,ENBiographies.licence_attribution_url,ENBiographies.licence_type,ENBiographies.licence_url,ENBiographies.licence_version) VALUES ('myspace','ARNKYES1187FB45230','.. .... .. .. .. .. .. .. .... ......',true,'http://www.myspace.com/thecallahan','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBiographies (ENBiographies.site,ENBiographies.artist_id,ENBiographies.desc,ENBiographies.truncated,ENBiographies.url,ENBiograp