personal, not unlike <span>Callahan\'s</span> songwriting. His answers reinforced the perception that Callahan is a serious, but free-thinking individual, not a purposefully disconnected artist as he is often portrayed. He is currently on a short U.S. tour, and will be playing Chicago\'s Garfield Park Conservatory on 5/6. We will be there. Frontier Psychiatrist:','http://frontpsych.com/2013/04/29/the-cul-de-sac-of-life-an-interview-with-bill-callahan/','2013-04-29T00:00:00','2013-04-29T04:17:12');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('daebc76c2226766f88f85448df3b82a9','ARP47F81187B9981F9','Music: Hear This: On “All Your Women Things,” Smog schools listeners on love, loss, and breasts','and while they\'re all pretty goddamn good, all the music kind of blends together (in my mind, at least) to form this serene but beautiful clump of melancholy tracks. That\'s how, even though I\'ve been listening to 1997\'s Red Apple Falls pretty much exclusively lately, I\'ve found myself obsessed once again with \"All Your Women Things\" off 1996\'s The Doctor Came At Dawn. <span>Callahan\'s</span> ode to lingerie, \"All Your Women Things\" is a nearly 7-minute master class on how to write a song about love, loss ...Read more Music: Hear This: On “All Your Women Things,” Smog schools listeners on love, loss, and breasts','http://www.avclub.com/articles/on-all-your-women-things-smog-schools-listeners-on,96123/?utm_medium=RSS&utm_campaign=feeds&utm_source=avclub_rss_daily','2013-04-08T00:00:00','2013-04-08T18:30:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('0418b7192c752c92ee7dbf685497b1eb','ARP47F81187B9981F9','Ovechkin Penalties Spur Rangers&#8217; 4-1 Win Over Caps','first goal of the season, beating goaltender Braden Holtby glove-side to make the score 2-1 befo