ins a legacy of the Inquisition along with the cryptic messages left by its victims. Back at her childhood home in California, Carvajal uncovers papers documenting a family of Carvajals who were burned at the stake in the 16th-century territory of Mexico. Could the author\'s family history be linked to the hidden history of <span>Arcos</span>? And could the unfortunate Carvajals have been her ancestors? Favorite Jewliciousy Books of 2012','http://www.jewlicious.com/2012/12/favorite-jewliciousy-books-of-2012/','2012-12-15T00:00:00','2012-12-15T00:19:27');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('592e1ebf9a16766e17288a3612421d10','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C','Bandas do Lollapalooza 2013 farão shows em clubes do Rio de Janeiro e São Paulo','Club. As apresentações acontecem nos dias 28, 29, 30 março e 1° de abril. Os ingressos começam a ser vendidos já na segunda-feira, 10/12, e custarão R$ 150,00 (com meia-entrada de R$ 75,00). ::Serviço:: Lolla Brasil Side Shows - SP 28/03 - Passion Pit 29/03 - Hot Chip 30/03 - Of Monsters and Men 31/03 - Alabama Shakes Local: Grand Metrópole - Av. São Luís, 187 - República Lolla Brasil Side Shows - RJ 28/03 - Hot Chip 26/03 - Two Door Cinema Club 30/03 - Passion Pit 01/04 - Alabama Shakes Local: Circo Voador - Rua dos <span>Arcos</span>, s/n - Lapa Bandas do Lollapalooza 2013 farão shows em clubes do Rio de Janeiro e São Paulo','http://www.rocknbeats.com.br/2012/12/08/bandas-do-lollapalooza-2013-farao-shows-em-clubes-do-rio-de-janeiro-e-sao-paulo/','2012-12-09T00:00:00','2012-12-08T14:27:46');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('7a607895c0eb91963edb382487bdb906','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C','Book events in La Verne Nov. and Dec.','(Twin Peaks and screenwriter for Fantastic Four and Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer!) sto