f a song at time ever since. Like a lot of bands resuscitating this era, Beach Party doesn\'t seem to aspire to much more than -- as their chorus shouts -- \"C\'mon, c\'mon, let\'s have some fun.\" As long as the hangover remedies work,','http://buzzbands.la/2012/11/02/ears-wide-open-beach-party/','2012-11-03T00:00:00','2012-11-02T22:19:56');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('59a567a6b7feac2402c64823d02cd07b','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C','Vuelve Kate Nash a Argentina y celebra Halloween con un nuevo video','A menos de dos años de su primera visita a la Argentina, Kate Nash se presentará el 4 de noviembre en The Roxy <span>Arcos</span> para dar inicio a la edición 2012 del Personal Fest.Su primera vez en Buenos Aires fue en febrero de 2011 en el Teatro Coliseo con My Best Friend is You, su segundo disco. Ahora, se hará cargo de la apertura oficial del Personal Fest 2012 que reunirá a Fiona Apple, Dirty Projectors, Kings of Leon, James Murphy, Clap Your Hands Say Yeah, Illya Kuryaki and the Valderramas, Babasónicos y muchos más.Antes de su vuelta para Argentina Kate Nash decidió festejar Halloween disfrazándose de vampiro','http://www.indiehearts.com/news/vuelve-kate-nash-a-argentina-y-celebra-halloween-con-un-nuevo-video/','2012-11-02T00:00:00','2012-11-02T17:21:04');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('4bfb07aa8f6443862962b06d509a90d0','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C','Ears Wide Open: Birds of a Black Feather','Sibling sparks fly in the music of Birds of a Black Feather, the new Los Angeles quintet built around the sweet/tart vocals of sisters Katie and Sarah Virden. The sisters, along with guitarist Murray Foretich and bassist Adam <span>Arcos</span>, deal in indie blues that ranges from teeth-rattling (\"Turn Me On\" and \"Say What You Mean\") to twangy and affecting (\"Freeway\"). The band has no formal releases yet -- a full-length is in the works -- but their early live shows, and something in the way the imperative \"Say What You Mean\" is delivered, mark them as a band you\'ll want to strap on your boots to see. ||| Download:','http://buzzbands.la/2012/10/30/ears-wide-open-birds-of-a-black-feather/','2012-10-30T00:00:00','2012-10-30T23:41:18');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('425de951a508289bb610e00b895e738a','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C','Rethink Your Approach To Statement Jewelry With Stone & Honey','Stone & Honey is the Portland-based brand well-known for translating natural elements into creative, simple jewelry. And, while crystals and marbled stones were the go-to materials of the past, the label\'s latest collection, <span>Arcos</span>, is all about rustic takes on geometric shapes. Hammered loops become like flattened rainbows, and linen-wrapped copper ovals are the hoop earrings for a different generation. The designs also feature belly-button-grazing necklaces as the new kind of statement necklace -- one that doesn\'t need sparkle or loud color to command attention. What else are we loving','http://www.refinery29.com/stone-and-honey?utm_source=feed&utm_medium=atom','2012-10-21T00:00:00','2012-10-21T20:02:12');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('454529abd94a3d760a1649468bc01e26','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C','Obituary: Anders Eliasson, composer','sound world, marked out by its marrying of emotion and tension - expressive but taut, regimented but never constricted, with no wasted notes and a discipline which reflected the Baroque music and jazz Eliasson so loved. At the time of his death he was composer-in-residence at the New York-based <span>Arcos</span> Orchestra. There was a feeling that Eliasson felt himself somehow at odds with the more esoteric elements of the compositional community. That feeling is encapsulated in the account of his arrival at the Sibelius Academy in Helsinki in 1993 to begin a stint as guest professor of composition. \'I\'m','http://www.gramophone.co.uk/classical-music-news/obituary-anders-eliasson-composer','2013-05-22T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('1cb3c44dedba43c3258002b248df3a63','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C','Classical music steps into the spotlight at midem 2013','will host a series of 10 conference sessions focusing on a host of different topics that go together to create the classical scene. Among the panellists will be Jim Selby, CEO of Naxos USA, Didier Martin, director of Naïve Classique (Gramophone\'s 2012 Label of the Year), Mickaël <span>Arcos</span>, software engineer at Abeille Musique, Jerald Miller, founder and president of Nu Jazz Entertainment, Matthias Röder, director of the Karajan Institute and Niall O\'Rourke, creative director of Decca Classics. Lang Lang will deliver the keynote address on \'Visionary Monday\' and talk about his mission as a true','http://www.gramophone.co.uk/classical-music-news/classical-music-steps-into-the-spotlight-at-midem-2013','2012-10-23T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('02083adcdfe58220d2b066c7dd6311d4','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C','National Book Award Finalists Announced','Boy Kings of Texas Robert Caro - The Passage of Power Katherine Boo - Behind the Beautiful Forevers Anthony Shadid - House of Stone Poetry David Ferry - Bewilderment: New Poems and Translations Cynthia Huntington - Heavenly Bodies Tim Seibles - Fast Animal Alan Shapiro - Night of the Republic Susan Wheeler - Meme Young People\'s Literature William Alexander - Goblin Secrets Carrie <span>Arcos</span> - Out of Reach Patricia McCormick - Never Fall Down Eliot Schrefer - Endangered Steve Sheinkin - Bomb: The Race to Build -- and Steal -- the World\'s Most Dangerous Weapons National Book Award Finalists Announced','http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2012/10/national-book-award-finalists-announced.html','2012-10-10T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('a12f1e1976f1ae26319e7162bfc0d27f','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C','Pop music these days: it all sounds the same, survey reveals','have published a new report on songs released between 1955 and 2010, showing the \"diversity of ... note combinations ... has consistently diminished in the last 50 years\". Measuring the Evolution of Contemporary Western Popular Music, by Joan Serrà, Álvaro Corral, Marián Boguñá, Martín Haro and Josep Ll <span>Arcos</span>, appears in the journal Scientific Reports . The researchers used a dataset of 464,411 music recordings to analyse what has changed - and what has stayed the same - over the past half-century of song. \"Many of [music\'s] patterns and metrics have been consistently stable for [this] period,\"','http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2012/jul/27/pop-music-sounds-same-survey-reveals','2012-07-27T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBiographies (ENBiographies.site,ENBiographies.artist_id,ENBiographies.desc,ENBiographies.truncated,ENBiographies.url,ENBiographies.licence_attribution,ENBiographies.licence_attribution_url,ENBiographies.licence_type,ENBiographies.licence_url,ENBiographies.licence_version) VALUES ('ilike','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C','i dont know',true,'http://www.ilike.com/artist/Marcos','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENTerms (ENTerms.name,ENTerms.artist_id,ENTerms.frequency,ENTerms.weight) VALUES ('electronic','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C',0.9383754455591139,0.875);INSERT IGNORE INTO ENTerms (ENTerms.name,ENTerms.artist_id,ENTerms.frequency,ENTerms.weight) VALUES ('synthpop','ARSXAAC12CEB275E9C',0.4482841136347961,0.75);INSERT IGNORE INTO ENT