s in their dates of emergence and geographic location the rhythms, melodic contours and internal harmonic relationships of our sources are all formed from common material and from a shared human understanding.In using these forms and sounds as a point of departure we hope to explore an enduring substratum in which resonant archetypes can be approached and combined in a meaningful way, applicable to our times  Donald Mason: Percussion Sian Ashby: Clarinet Ian Tothill: Fiddle/Viola Graham Wright: Bagpipes/Programming Andrew Wood: Keyboards/Didgeridoo Abdezzahid Haddani: Djembe/Frame Drum',0,'http://www.last.fm/music/Arcomnia/+wiki','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBiographies (ENBiographies.site,ENBiographies.artist_id,ENBiographies.desc,ENBiographies.truncated,ENBiographies.url,ENBiographies.licence_attribution,ENBiographies.licence_attribution_url,ENBiographies.licence_type,ENBiographies.licence_url,ENBiographies.licence_version) VALUES ('myspace','ARIVBVJ12DE7790AB5','object classid=\'clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\' id=\'Slideshow\' width=\'300\' height=\'228\'>.............. .. .. .. .. .. ...',true,'http://www.myspace.com/arcomnia','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBiographies (ENBiographies.site,ENBiographies.artist_id,ENBiographies.desc,ENBiographies.truncated,ENBiographies.url,ENBiographies.licence_attribution,ENBiographies.licence_attribution_url,ENBiographies.licence_type,ENBiographies.licence_url,ENBiographies.licence_version) VALUES ('facebook','ARIVBVJ12DE7790AB5','ARCOMNIA The musical style of Arcomnia is arrived by combining ...',true,'http://graph.facebook.com/355923775248','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENTerms (ENTerms.name,ENTerms.artist_id,ENTerms.frequency,ENTerms.weight) VALUES ('dubstep','ARIVBVJ12DE7790AB5',0.33022721221617884,0.5);INSERT IGNORE INTO ENTerms (ENTerms.name,ENTerms.artist_id,ENTerms.frequency,ENTerms.weight) VALUES ('swing','ARIVBVJ12DE7790AB5',0.3379662007226162,0.4166666666666667);INSERT IGNORE INTO ENUr