r album Agitor Lucens V was presented in Paris, London, Rome and Buenos Aires with a ballet directed by renowned Argentinean choreographer Oscar Arαiz.  Ara and Danais Tokatlian, founders and main composers of Arco Iris, moved to California in 1978, making a 100 year old log cabin in the mountain community of Blue Jay, their new home.  Since 1979, Ara and Danais with the collaboration of world class musicians like Milcho Leviev, Alex Acuρa, Chester Thompson, Chris Rhyne, Julio Ledezma, Bill Fowler, Hartt Stearns, James Zota Baker, Julio Figueroa and Pablo Allende, developed a musical language where freedom of statement, a deep spiritual message and a unique blend of jazz, rock and South American folk music became the key ingredients of their compositions. This innovative sound is captured in a new set of Arco Iris recordings: Amigos, Fiesta, Exploring South America, Blue Pheasant, Alive in Venice, Peace Will Save the Rainbow, Condor, In Memoriam, Arco Iris En Vivo Hoy and Peace Pipes, the latest reaching # 17 in the Jazz Top-40 radio airplay list.  Ara Tokatlian has participated in the recording of numerous film scores including Out on a Limb with Shirley McLaine, Courage featuring Sofia Loren, Extreme Prejudice with Nick Nolte, The Telephone with Whoopi Goldberg, Stand and Deliver with Edward James Olmos, Bat 21 starring Gene Hackman and Kingjite with Charles Bronson, working with composers such as Ry Cooder, Craig Safan, Chris Young and fellow Argentinean Lalo Schiffrin. Ara is also a prolific composer for documentaries and TV commercials. In 1995, Ara toured Europe as a member of Harry Belafonte�s band.  Over the past 20 years, Arco Iris has been part of the Los Angeles Music Center on Tour and the Orange County Performing Art Center, providing hundreds of cultural performances for audiences in Southern California. In 1997 this work earned Arco Iris the Lifetime Achievement Award: P.A.S.A. (Professional Artists in Schools Award).  Arco Iris performs throughout the United States and Argentina in clubs, festivals and special concerts at venues such as the River Plate Soccer Stadium, Teatro San Martin, Dorothy Chandler Pavilion, John Anson Ford Amphitheater, Mark Taper Forum, Shrine Auditorium and the Hollywood Bowl.  With deep respect and appreciation for the instruments, rhythms and sounds of the world�s diverse cultures, Arco Iris, Spanish for rainbow, is an exhilarating, uplifting and magical musical experience.',0,'http://www.last.fm/music/Arcoiris/+wiki','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBiographies (ENBiographies.site,ENBiographies.artist_id,ENBiographies.desc,ENBiographies.truncated,ENBiographies.url,ENBiographies.licence_attribution,ENBiographies.licence_attribution_url,ENBiographies.licence_type,ENBiographies.licence_url,ENBiographies.licence_version) VALUES ('myspace','AR7U2QE1187FB3A651','.. ..........................Myspace Layouts.... - ....Retro Myspace Layouts..........Myspace Codes.... - ....Myspace ...',true,'http://www.myspace.com/arcoirisdisco','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENTerms (ENTerms.name,ENTerms.artist_id,ENTerms.frequency,ENTerms.weight) VALUES ('blues','AR7U2QE1187FB3A651',1,1);INSERT IGNORE INTO ENTerms (ENTerms.name,ENTerms.artist_id,ENTerms.frequency,ENTerms.weight) VALUES ('electronica','AR7U2QE1187FB3A651',0.32746527036428363,0.45098039215686275);INSERT IGNORE INTO ENTerms (ENTerms.name,ENTerms.artist_id,ENTerms.frequency,ENTerms.weight) VALUES ('techno','AR7U2QE1187FB3A651',0.3434750052658757,0.4411764705882353);INSERT IGNORE INTO ENTerms (ENTerms.name,ENTerms.artist_id,ENTerms.frequency,ENTerms.weight) VALUES ('rock','AR7U2QE1187FB3A651',0.20712018237027915,0.13725490196078433);INSERT IGNORE INTO ENTerms (ENTerms.name,ENTerms.artist_id,ENTerms.frequency,ENTerms.weight) VALUES ('jazz rock','AR7U2QE1187FB3A651',0.06762181845559408,0.12745098039215685);INSERT IGNORE INTO ENUrls (ENUrls.site,ENUrls.artist_id,ENUrls.url) VALUES ('itunes','AR7U2QE1187FB3A651','http://itunes.com/Arcoiris')