Sci Fi it didn\'t really seem like much more than reverberating noise rattling out of my wagon\'s stock speakers. After that initial rebuffing, I gave Arco Flute Foundation another shot on the home stereo in much higher fidelity, but again there were no dice...','http://www.lostatsea.net/LAS/archives/reviews/records/arcoflutefoundation_everythingafterthebombisscifi.jpg','http://www.lostatsea.net/review.phtml?id=34570126841764fbd15fb4','2009-10-30T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('ARTG2M81187FB3A5BB','the arco flute foundation - everything after everything after the bomb is sci-fi (from Mimaroglu)','everything after everything after the bomb is sci-fi','arco flute foundation, the everything after everything after the bomb is sci-fi cd [mf19]  the arco flute foundation formed in 1999 when two-thirds of pittsburgh\'s minimalist drumless rock trio meisha moved to edinboro, pa to attend the small state university located there. with little else to do in this sleepy farm town, mike tamburo and pete spynda devoted themselves to this new band with matt mcdowell and jeff komara...','http://www.mimaroglumusicsales.com/g/mf19cd.jpg','http://www.mimaroglumusicsales.com/artists/the+arco+flute+foundation.html#the%20arco%20flute%20foundation__everything%20after%20everything%20after%20the%20bomb%20is%20sci-fi_PR','2009-07-17T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('ARTG2M81187FB3A5BB','the arco flute foundation - quantum heresy (from Mimaroglu)','quantum heresy','matt mcdowell - quantum heresy cd-r  matt mcdowell first came to notoriety as a member of the arco flute foundation and has appeared in a variety of projects mostly emanating from his home of portland, or.  the mystical energy of his west coast surroundings comes forth in these four solo electric guitar pieces, recalling the density of rhys chatham and the velocity of loren mazzacane connors (though filtered through his own phlegmatic vision)  .....','http://www.mimaroglumusicsales.com/g/sharks5cd.jpg','http://www.mimaroglumusicsales.com/artists/the+arco+flute+foundation.html#the%20arco%20flute%20foundation__quantum%20heresy_PR','2009-07-10T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('ARTG2M81187FB3A5BB','Arco Flute Foundation - Everything After the Bomb Is Sci-Fi (from pitchfork)','Everything After the Bomb Is Sci-Fi','I suppose you could bow a flute if you wanted to.  I\'m not really sure what    kind of sound it would make, or if it would make any sound at all.  Hence    my confusion and amusement at this band\'s name.  In musical notation, \'arco\'    means \'played with the bow,\' as in a violin, bass, viola or cello (or maybe    a guitar for you adventurous types)...','http://pitchfork-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/albums/279/cover-homepage_large.jpg','http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/280-everything-after-the-bomb-is-sci-fi/','2009-06-08T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('ARTG2M81187FB3A5BB','Arco Flute Foundation - Everything After The Bomb Is Sci-Fi. (from Splendid Magazine)','Everything After The Bomb Is Sci-Fi.','Practitioners of an experimental brand of instrumental rock neither captivating nor ground-breaking, Pennsylvania\'s Arco Flute Foundation (whose members also play in the decidedly more nuanced and ambiently-inclined Meisha) suffer from the traps of participating in a movement that both shuns the conventions of traditional songwriting and desires to attract an audience attuned to such sounds...','http://www.splendidezine.com/reviews/jul-1-02/arco.gif','http://www.splendidezine.com/review.html?reviewid=32337741211018511','2009-02-26T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('ARTG2M81187FB3A5BB','Arco Flute Foundation - Everything After the Bomb Is Sci-Fi (from Pitchfork)','Everything After the Bomb Is Sci-Fi','I suppose you could bow a flute if you wanted to.  I\'m not really sure what\n    kind of sound it would make, or if it would make any sound at all.  Hence\n    my confusion and amusement at this band\'s name.  In musical notation, \'arco\'\n    means \'played with the bow,\' as in a violin, bass, viola or cello (or maybe\n    a guitar for you adventurous types)...','http://assets1.pitchforkmedia.com/images/original/9272.everything-after-the-bomb-is-sci-fi.gif','http://www.pitchforkmedia.com/article/record_review/15034-arco-flute-foundation-everything-after-the-bomb-is-sci-fi','2008-07-30T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBiographies (ENBiographies.site,ENBiographies.artist_id,ENBiographies.desc,ENBiographies.truncated,ENBiographies.url,ENBiographies.licence_attribution,ENBiographies.licence_attribution_url,ENBiographies.licence_type,ENBiographies.licence_url,ENBiographies.licence_version) VALUES ('aol','ARTG2M81187FB3A5BB','When not recording or performing as Meisha, Pittsburgh-area experimental rock ...',true,'http://music.aol.com/artist/arco-flute-foundation/biography','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBiographies (ENBiographies.site,ENBiographies.artist_id,ENBiographies.desc,ENBiographies.truncated,ENBiographies.url,ENBiographies.licence_attribution,ENBiographies.licence_attribution_url,ENBiographies.licence_type,ENBiographies.licence_url,ENBiographies.licence_version) VALUES ('myspace','ARTG2M81187FB3A5BB','the arco flute foundation formed in 1999 when two-thirds of ...',true,'http://www.myspace.com/arcoflute','','','','','');INSERT IGNORE INTO EN