tire career; concert-goers can obviously expect songs from Blur and Gorillaz, and perhaps even some from <span>The Good, the Bad & the Queen</span> and his operas. Touching on the Blur album, Albarn called it \"a definite possibility\". \"We\'ve got a couple of occasions when we\'re stuck in the middle of nowhere,\" he said. \"So we might make the record in a week. If we can, it would be nice.\" So while the China recording','http://www.obscuresound.com/2013/05/blurs-damon-albarn-talks-solo-release-new-blur-album/','2013-05-28T00:00:00','2013-05-28T15:35:03');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('17824c457f7f1ef602a544d88f680fdf','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Magnetic North und Sarah Neufeld live @ Volksbühne, Berlin | 19.05.2013','ein Gewitter ausbrechen - wenn auch nur ein orchestrales. Die Musik des Hauptacts The Magnetic North beeindruckte und ließ sich mit wenig anderem vergleichen, dabei handelt es sich lediglich um ein Side-Projekt der drei Hauptprotagonisten Simon Tong (The Verve, <span>The Good, the Bad & the Queen</span>), Gawain Erland Cooper (Erland & The Carneval) und der elfenhaften Allerounderin Hannah Peel. Ein Chor bestehend aus 20 schlagkräftigen Stimmen, ein Cello, drei Violinen, drei Blasinstrumente und ein Schlagzeuger mit rotgeringelten Drumsticks ergänzten dieses sich durch endlos schöne, gigantische','http://rockzoom.de/the-magnetic-north-und-sarah-neufeld-live-volksbuhne-berlin-19-05-2013/','2013-06-03T00:00:00','2013-05-25T21:33:21');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('bd3d1feb46a37c3405558f03a29ef322','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Magnetic North und Sarah Neufeld live @ Volksbühne, Berlin | 19.05.2013','ein Gewitter ausbrechen - wenn auch nur ein orchestrales. Die Musik des Hauptacts The Magnetic North beeindruckte und ließ sich mit wenig anderem vergleichen, dabei handelt es sich lediglich um ein Side-Projekt der drei Hauptprotagonisten Simon Tong (The Verve, <span>The Good, the Bad & the Queen</span>), Gawain Erland Cooper (Erland & The Carneval) und der elfenhaften Allerounderin Hannah Peel. Ein Chor bestehend aus 20 schlagkräftigen Stimmen, ein Cello, drei Violinen, drei Blasinstrumente und ein Schlagzeuger mit rotgeringelten Drumsticks ergänzten dieses sich durch endlos schöne, gigantische','http://rockzoom.de/2013/05/25/the-magnetic-north-und-sarah-neufeld-live-volksbuhne-berlin-19-05-2013/','2013-05-27T00:00:00','2013-05-25T21:33:21');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('8a03ff3648822267404008887eef2373','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','Album Reviews:  The Child Of Lov - The Child Of Lov','Child Of Lov\'s impressively sleek falsetto delivery and by the time you\'re eased into his vocals he raises the pace with the urgent and spiky \'Heal\'. Damon Albarn lends his voice, and some sombre keyboard tones, on third track \'One Day\', leaving the sense of a funkier <span>The Good, The Bad And The Queen</span>. It finds its highest gear with aplomb for fifth and sixth tracks \'Give Me\' and \'Go With The Wind\', the former an experimental dance-funk extravaganza propelled by a jittery riff and intriguing percussion building to an anthemic chorus, the latter starting with casual beeps and tones before spiralling','http://www.thisisfakediy.co.uk/articles/albums/the-child-of-lov-the-child-of-lov','2013-04-30T00:00:00','2013-04-30T14:00:55');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('4ad94b89ce4d45e2cf63c9407ccc4a8e','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','90s Britpop/Indie Rock Band Blur Announces first studio album in 10 Years','are set to headline Belgium\'s Rock Werchter as well as perform at the Spanish and Portuguese dates of the Primavera Sound Festival, as well as America\'s Coachella. Frontman Damon Albarn has been evolved in Different Music Projects, Included \"Gorillaz\" (2001) (With help by British Animator Jamie Hewlett), \"<span>The Good, the Bad and the Queen</span>\" (2007) with Tony Allen, Paul Simonon and Simon Tong. and \"Rocket Juice & the Moon\" (2012) with Tony Allen, and Flea from Red Hot Chili Peppers. Guitarist Graham Coxon also started a Solo Career which he had released Eight Solo Albums Starting in 1998 with \"The Sky','http://current.com/entertainment/music/94092500_90s-britpop-indie-rock-band-blur-announces-first-studio-album-in-10-years.htm?xid=RSSfeed','2013-04-07T00:00:00','2013-04-06T23:59:23');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('f0d7885f6e18ab506957eb704536d464','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','Nuevo video de Bobby Womack','extendida.\"Ahora Bobby Womack ha vuelto con su última grabación propia, después de casi 18 años de ausencia: The Bravest Man In The Universe. Detrás de este disco, vale resaltar, está el británico Damon Albarn: polifacético cantante de Blur, quien a pesar de tener una decena proyectos (desde sus bandas Gorillaz, <span>The Good, The Bad & The Queen</span>, Rocket Juice & The Moon, hasta su deficiente disco en solitario), ha colaborado en la producción de éste, el más reciente disco de Womack.\" Reseña de The Bravest Man In The Universe de Bobby Womack.De este nuevo grupo de temas se desprende \"It\'s Been A Long Night\", el cual fue','http://www.revistametronomo.com/2013/03/25/nuevo-video-de-bobby-womack/','2013-03-26T00:00:00','2013-03-26T03:40:50');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('95a14bef1578035b74633c9ee3b9c785','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','Eurockéennes 2013 : les premiers noms !','inv