ent on hiatus so its members could pursue other projects. They reunited in 2008 and started playing live in 2009. The band then released two tracks, \'The Puritan\' and \'Under the Westway\', last year. Despite their continued touring Damon - who is also a member of Rocket Juice and the Moon, Gorillaz and <span>The Good, The Bad and the Queen</span> - has always been hesitant for them to make a new album. He said: \'\'There\'s a part of me that would love to be able to bring it into our 40s and our sort of family world. But does it belong in that world? That\'s the other side of it. Do any of us need that? And','http://www.virginmedia.com/music/news/story/2013/05/07/blur-recroding-new-album/','2013-05-07T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('a562207cc11fb11498c325e5c0f4186f','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','Blur recroding new album','drummer Dave Rowntree - went on hiatus so its members could pursue other projects. They reunited in 2008 and started playing live in 2009. The band then released two tracks, \'The Puritan\' and \'Under the Westway\', last year. Despite their continued touring Damon - who is also a member of Rocket Juice and the Moon, Gorillaz and <span>The Good, The Bad and the Queen</span> - has always been hesitant for them to make a new album. He said: \'\'There\'s a part of me that would love to be able to bring it into our 40s and our sort of family world. But does it belong in that world? That\'s the other side of it. Do any of us need that? And','http://www.tourdates.co.uk/news/22890-blur-recroding-new-album','2013-05-07T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('43530bc2f7fc3dd872760eb3f87b3881','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','Coachella 2013: Blur, How to Destroy Angels, Yeah Yeah Yeahs turn it up','band, although one with more commercial cache in the States. Blur, in their first show in the U.S. since their 2008 reunion, reminded music fans why they left most Britpop bands in the dust in the late nineties. The band\'s arrival at Coachella was a long time coming. Ace guitarist Graham Coxon left the band in 2002, during the recording of their seventh album \"Think Tank.\" Blur played Coachella that year -- sans Coxon -- and frontman Damon Albarn has since returned with side projects Gorillaz and <span>The Good, the Bad and the Queen</span>. Coachella 2013: Blur, How to Destroy Angels, Yeah Yeah Yeahs turn it up','http://www.hitfix.com/news/coachella-2013-blur-how-to-destroy-angels-yeah-yeah-yeahs-turn-it-up','2013-04-13T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('51c14f6b73541cea3534a0c2d1d628b6','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','How To Buy... Blur & Solo','since suggesting great new heights are theirs for the taking, if they want it. Until then, which of their albums are the ones you need? The Britpop-era favourite Parklife, say, or its predecessor, Modern Life Is Rubbish? Later period works such as 13 or Think Tank? Leisure or Blur? Anyone fancy remix/ live curio Bustin\' + Dronin\'? There are the solo records and band recordings by Damon Albarn - where do <span>The Good, The Bad & The Queen</span> and Gorillaz fit in - and Graham Coxon\'s LPs. T Tell us what you think, please, and the best suggestions will appear in the next issue of MOJO. Thank you! How To Buy... Blur & Solo','http://www.mojo4music.com/blog/2013/02/how_to_buy_blur_solo.html','2013-02-27T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('2d585257717101c509580de758efb5a0','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','Ray Davies pretends to be Damon','don\'t want anyone to see me. People say, \'Who are you?\' they know me but they don\'t know my name. I tell them I\'m Damon Albarn and put on a cockney accent.\'\' Ray, 68, also said he has little care for the records Damon makes with Blur and his many other projects - which include Gorillaz and <span>The Good, the Bad and the Queen</span> - as he doesn\'t see them as being about ordinary people in the same way his own work is. Talking about The Kinks 1978 album, \'Misfits\', he added to Q magazine: \'\'I don\'t care about what Damon does, I care about real people. \'Misfits\' is about a friend of mine who passed away recently. I\'m just trying','http://www.virginmedia.com/music/news/story/2012/08/05/ray-davies-pretends-to-be/','2012-08-05T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('13bd1e7eb920277c60a0a6b94e71b898','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','Albarn has \'more interesting\' projects than Blur','constantly asked about it and I don\'t really know. \'\'I don\'t want to just do gigs. I want to do something that has some genuine resonance, and helps explain to me why I\'m there. Something that explains to everyone in the field [watching the band] while they\'re there. I do believe in the spirit, it\'s what drives me.\'\' Damon\'s other projects include supergroup Rocket Juice and the Moon, Gorillaz, <span>The Good, The Bad and the Queen</span> and his opera Dr Dee. Blur will headline a special concert in London\'s Hyde Park to celebrate the closing of the Olympics on August 12. Albarn has \'more interesting\' projects than Blur','http://www.virginmedia.com/music/news/story/2012/07/31/albarn-has-more-interesting/','2012-07-31T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, The Bad and The Queen - The Good, The Bad and The Queen (from Soundspike)','The Good, The Bad and The Queen','This concoction--anchored by the ample talents of frontman Damon Albarn (Blur, Gorillaz) with Simon Tong (The Verve) on guitar, Paul Simonon (The Clash) on bass, Afro-beat great Tony Allen on drums and the stunningly creative producer Danger Mouse behind the boards--nearly lives up to the sum of its parts. Despite the names on the credits, \" The Good, The Bad and The Queen\" is by no means a beat-driven affair; it\'s all about setting a mood...','','http://www.soundspike.com/news/2/11453-the_good_the_bad_and_the_queen_news_album_review_the_good_the_bad.html','2010-12-07T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, The Bad And The Queen - The Good, The Bad And The Queen (from Gigwise)','The Good, The Bad And The Queen','The Good, The Bad And The Queen\'s eagerly awaited eponymously titled debut album is at last upon us and proof, if any were needed, that Damon Albarn can seemingly do no wrong. What initially began as a solo project for the former Blur front man, soon developed into a super-group of sorts...','','http://www.gigwise.com/reviews/albums/27011/The-Good-The-Bad-And-The-Queen-&#8211;-The-Good-The-Bad-And-The-Queen-Parlophone-Released-220107','2010-11-23T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, The Bad & The Queen - The Good, The Bad & The Queen (from Hour)','The Good, The Bad & The Queen','Clash bassist Paul Simonon and Blur vocalist Damon Albarn wouldn\'t seem to have a lot in common on first glance, but here is a pairing that, like peanut butter and bananas (respectively), actually works for the most part. (That said, there is some supremely self-indulgent garbage on here: Three Changes and anything that prominently features the autistic-chimp-like piano playing of Albarn...','http://www.hour.ca/_images/montreal/1505/texte/spin_thegoodthebad.jpg','http://www.hour.ca/music/spin.aspx?iIDDisque=4112','2010-11-02T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, The Bad & The Queen - The Good, The Bad & The Queen (from MusicOMH)','The Good, The Bad & The Queen','1994. The Conservative government is floundering, there\'s a bright new attractive Leader Of The Opposition to entrust all our hopes and dreams in, and there\'s an overwhelming feeling of optimism on the streets. Blur\'s Parklife is the soundtrack of the year, and its witty, deceptively upbeat songs blare from every car window and shop changing room. 2007...','http://www.musicomh.com/albums/albums_images/good-bad-queen.jpg','http://www.musicomh.com/albums/good-bad-queen_0107.htm','2010-08-23T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, the Bad and the Queen - The Good, the Bad and the Queen (from Blender)','The Good, the Bad and the Queen','After you\'ve been a Britpop titan, cartoon rock star and holder of the Guinness record for best-selling album (by a virtual band), your next move can be elusive. Blur singer/Gorillaz founder Damon Albarn formed his third group by scanning credits on fave albums and making some calls...','','http://www.blender.com/guide/reviews.aspx?id=4340','2010-08-22T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, The Bad And The Queen - Herculean (from Launch)','Herculean','In another universe, this would be the new Blur single. This gloriously atmosphere mélange of 21st century dub and traditional English songwriting is certainly what Damon was inching towards on the under-rated \"Think Tank\" album. But since the departure of Graham Coxon, fashion and credibility have decreed Blur a spent force - if you imagine a new Blur single, it\'s an inherently half-hearted, lukewarm affair. So the new Blur single comes out under a pseudonym, with a cast of supporting players...','http://d.yimg.com/eur.yimg.com/xp/dotmusic/20061103/18/443615727.jpg','http://uk.launch.yahoo.com/061103/33/20ujj.html','2009-12-18T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','the good the bad and the queen - The Good, The Bad And The Queen (from ultimate-guitar)','The Good, The Bad And The Queen','Sound: If you were a fan of vocalist Daron Albarn\'s work in the Gorillaz or Blur for that matter, then you probably already know that the singer never likes to stick with the same sound, which is a massive part of his appeal. The Good, The Bad & The Queen might seem risky in some fans\' eyes, with its stripped-down sound. It bares absolutely no resemblance to the more electronic-oriented Gorillaz or more punk-rock driven Blur, and that\'s to be commended...','http://ultimate-guitar.com/reviews/images/10_13578_13579.jpg','http://www.ultimate-guitar.com/reviews/compact_discs/the_good_the_bad_and_the_queen/the_good_the_bad_and_the_queen/index.html','2009-11-15T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, the Bad & the Queen - The Good, the Bad & the Queen (from Lost At Sea)','The Good, the Bad & the Queen','For bottom-line types, the word on The Good, the Bad & the Queen can be condensed into \"Gorillaz without much high end,\" a dark, bummed out trip conjuring slow-mo video shots of Damon Albarn in a dark trench coat getting closer, then, poof!, closer as a factory in the background belches filth into the sky...','http://www.lostatsea.net/LAS/archives/reviews/records/goodbadqueen_st.jpg','http://www.lostatsea.net/review.phtml?id=173938004645be334cbb8f0','2009-10-30T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, The Bad & The Queen - The Good, The Bad, The Queen (from Delusions of Adequacy)','The Good, The Bad, The Queen','The self-titled record from Damon Albarn-led group The Good, The Bad, The Queen is remarkable in as many ways as it is disappointing. Disappointment was built into the infrastructure of this record. The cast of characters casts too large a shadow. Here we are nearly a month after its release and The Good, The Bad, The Queen was mildly received by Uncut magazine, and it sets on the lower echelon of the New Release shelf at my local record store...','http://www.adequacy.net/wp-content/uploads/images/covers/7702-Cover.jpg','http://www.adequacy.net/2007/03/the-good-the-bad-aamp-the-queen-the-good-the-bad-the-queen/','2009-07-21T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, The Bad & The Queen - The Good, The Bad & The Queen (from No Ripcord)','The Good, The Bad & The Queen','To begin things honestly, this album practically creaks from the case with the weight of its contributors\' reputations. When one of the major songwriters of the last fifteen years collaborates with arguably the most iconic bassist ever, notice is taken.  Add a particularly interesting, commercially successful producer and the \"supergroup\" tag appears. Tony Allen co-founded Afrobeat with Fela Kuti. Simon Tong? A band called the Verve... (It\'s good...) It\'s actually pretty good...','http://www.noripcord.com/files/imagecache/cover-image/files/albumreview/cover/530_large.jpg','http://www.noripcord.com/reviews/music/the-good-the-bad-the-queen/the-good-the-bad-the-queen','2009-07-21T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, The Bad & The Queen - The Good, The Bad & The Queen (from Launch)','The Good, The Bad & The Queen','When Blur launched \"Parklife\" in 1994, the press were serenaded by the band at a London greyhound track. Damon Albarn and Alex James presumably held court to the chuckling media through a succession of lagers, a cheeky line of coke in the bogs and a rambling speech of some considerable ambition and attitude from the singer...','http://d.yimg.com/eur.yimg.com/xp/dotmusic/20070125/18/141389063.jpg','http://uk.launch.yahoo.com/070125/33/2121y.html','2009-07-21T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, the Bad & the Queen - The Good, the Bad & the Queen (from Robert Christgau)','The Good, the Bad & the Queen','No text for this review; see http://robertchristgau.com/xg/bk-cg90/grades-90s.php.','','http://www.robertchristgau.com/get_artist.php?id=5740&name=The+Good%2C+the+Bad+%26+the+Queen#The%20Good%2C%20the%20Bad%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Queen__The%20Good%2C%20the%20Bad%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Queen','2009-07-10T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, The Bad & The Queen - The Good, The Bad & The Queen (from Alternative Press)','The Good, The Bad & The Queen','Blur\'s Think Tank \nGorillaz\' Gorillaz \nBlur\'s 13','http://www.altpress.com/images/reviews/reviews_TheGoodTheBadAndQue.gif','http://www.altpress.com/reviews/580.htm','2009-06-12T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, the Bad & the Queen - The Good The Bad And The Queen (from bbc)','The Good The Bad And The Queen','It\'s an electric period for listeners keen to understand England\'s capital city through popular music. Artists of all stripes are trying to encapsulate what it feels like to be part of the country\'s most filthy, frustrating, hilarious and exciting manor.  The Good, The Bad and The Queen are barely acquainted with the claustrophobic paranoia of Bloc Party, far removed from the brash, tongue-in-cheek street reportage of Jamie T and a million miles from Lily Allen\'s sweet ska-pop...','','http://www.bbc.co.uk/music/reviews/pfqv','2009-06-12T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENReviews (ENReviews.artist_id,ENReviews.name,ENReviews.release,ENReviews.summary,ENReviews.image_url,ENReviews.url,ENReviews.date_found) VALUES ('AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','The Good, the Bad and the Queen - The Good (from Stylus Magazine)','The Good',' ','http://www.stylusmagazine.com/images/reviews/g/good-the-bad-and-the-queen-the-st.jpg','http://www.stylusmagazine.com/reviews/the-good-the-bad-and-the-queen/the-good-the-bad-and-the-queen.htm','2009-06-08T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENAudios (ENAudios.audio_id,ENAudios.artist_id,ENAudios.title,ENAudios.length,ENAudios.url,ENAudios.date) VALUES ('12ceae004171826b3739b654c24d2c70','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','Mr. Whippy',195,'http://sonnyvenice.phpnet.org/musique/michto%20mu/10%202010/03-the_good,_the_bad_&_the_queen-mr._whippy.mp3','2010-10-25T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENAudios (ENAudios.audio_id,ENAudios.artist_id,ENAudios.title,ENAudios.length,ENAudios.url,ENAudios.date) VALUES ('12872ded9b8c90f35b75847b27ee4004','AR2A6UJ1187FB4BF5C','Nature Springs',0,'http://justsayinisall.com/music/More11-20/16Natu