RC81187FB49B20','New Oh, Sleeper Song \"The Pitch\"','Hit the replies to check out a new <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> song called \"The Pitch\" from their upcoming EP, Titan. Submitted by JayDanielHammer and rawspinner New <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> Song \"The Pitch\"','http://www.absolutepunk.net/showthread.php?t=3258311','2013-06-22T00:00:00','2013-06-22T20:46:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('231d9bd0ee7118a6990bcc2171d518d8','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','LYRIC VIDEO: Oh, Sleeper – “The Pitch” (Feat. Casey Sabol)','<span>Oh, Sleeper</span> have debuted a lyric video for their brand new single, \"The Pitch,\" which features guest vocals from former Periphery frontman Casey Sabol. The song comes from the group\'s forthcoming EP, TITAN. While there\'s no release date as of yet for the record, the group have confirmed it is slated to drop in the near future. Follow the jump to give \"The Pitch\" a listen and make sure to check out <span>Oh, Sleeper</span>\'s set if you\'re attending Vans Warped Tour this summer! ... LYRIC VIDEO: <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> – “The Pitch” (Feat. Casey Sabol)','http://www.underthegunreview.net/2013/06/22/lyric-video-oh-sleeper-the-pitch-feat-casey-sabol/','2013-06-22T00:00:00','2013-06-22T19:21:47');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('e0fe837926c5bbcbc97ef5e2028ea6b0','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','Oh, Sleeper Will Release Two New EPs','Due to the band\'s huge success with their Indiegogo campaign (making $24,000 or so over their goal), <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> have decided to release two EPs, instead of just one. They announced they will work on the details of getting in the studio to record the EP right after Warped Tour. They also plan on releasing a new single soon, titled \"The Pitch,\" so be sure to keep your eyes peeled for that new song! Read the full announcement from the band by taking a look below the jump. In case you missed it, <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> are on this year\'s Vans Warped Tour, so check them out when they hit your city! We have been at breakneck ... cannot wait to hear your response. We will release a single, \"THE PITCH,\" ASAP. We are getting all of the merchandise and everything else into production for all of the awesome funders. We\'ve never been in charge of doing ALL of this before haha, but it\'s an exciting challenge. Look for more updates! Due to the insane rush that we\'ve been experiencing in this time crunch, we haven\'t had a lot of time to make updates about the process, but we thank you so much for your patience. Stay tuned, The Titan EP is coming soon! And of course TITAN will be available to everyone soon! <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> Will Release Two New EPs','http://www.underthegunreview.net/2013/06/16/oh-sleeper-moving-will-release-two-new-eps/','2013-06-16T00:00:00','2013-06-16T20:11:53');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('2db5722c55ed1df37b12319ba3da1b03','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','UTG INTERVIEW: Jake Luhrs of heartsupport / August Burns Red','the community, we\'ve got contests, giveaways, merchandise, and we\'ll have Bibles and other books. I\'m bringing some books on sexual abuse victims, I\'m bringing books on God\'s Grace, we\'ve got Beau Bokan [of Blessthefall] who\'s going to be at the tent doing signings, we\'re going to be doing interviews with bands like <span>Oh, Sleeper...</span> and who knows, maybe we\'ve got Architects. We\'re getting a bunch of cool items from a lot of those bands that we\'re going to have signed and used as giveaways. Man, we\'ve got so much stuff. Honestly, it\'s ridiculous. It\'s going to be a good time. I think the bottom line is to','http://www.underthegunreview.net/2013/06/12/utg-interview-jake-luhrs-of-heartsupport-august-burns-red/','2013-06-13T00:00:00','2013-06-12T21:43:43');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('a634bc995b95cda73732d85f3fd44d78','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','VANS WARPED TOUR Announces Attractions And Activities','card on day-of-show at the tent. Bandhappy lessons SELL OUT FAST! Reserve your spot now. Lessons will be offered from members of Architects, August Burns Red, Blessthefall, Bring Me The Horizon, Crossfaith, Handguns, I See Stars, Ice Nine Kills, Like Moths To Flames, Memphis May Fire, <span>Oh, Sleeper</span>,, Silverstein, Stick To Your Guns, Story of the Year, Texas in July, Upon A Burning Body, VersaEmerge, Volumes, and many more! BANDHAPPY representatives will be on-site speaking with fans waiting in line and taking orders for lessons every morning. During lessons, students will be provided with','http://hangout.altsounds.com/news/159359-vans-warped-tour-announces-attractions-activities.html','2013-06-01T00:00:00','2013-05-31T21:46:56');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('5b2f8c2928e553e3582d4f677ea81bc5','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','Oh, Sleeper seeks funds for new EP and trailer and van repairs','<span>OH, SLEEPER</span> LAUNCH INDIEGOGO CAMPAIGN TO FUND NEW EP, NEW TRAILER & VAN REPAIRS!Fan incentive packages include all kinds of exclusive merchandise, getting on stage with the band, and more! http://igg.me/at/ohsleeper/x/1033060 After three successful full-length albums, <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> are asserting their independence and taking their career directly into the hands of their most dedicated fans. <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> fan devotion is so intense that many of them have tattooed the band\'s symbol, lyrics and artwork on their bodies, created fan artwork, and participated in the \"be that guy\" campaigns on ... Shirts, armbands, hoodies, original artwork from the band, a USB stick filled with unreleased demos, an invitation to the \"smash and burn\" party where fans can help wield axes and torches as they decimate the band\'s broken down trailer, the opportunity to join the band on-stage...the list goes on. <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> formed in 2006 from the ashes of the short-lived Tooth & Nail Records band Terminal. Kinard and ex-Between The Buried & Me guitarist Blay formed a quick chemistry and songwriting partnership that has endured through a few lineup changes, with Nate Grady recently moving from bass to guitar and ... 200 Albums\" chart, debuting at #12 on the \"Hard Rock Albums\" chart and #120 on the Pop charts. Children of Fire followed another conceptual story conceived by Kinard, producing the singles \"Endseekers\" and \"Hush Yael.\" The brand new concept EP the band will fund through the Indiegogo campaign brings <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> full circle. After all, their first release was an EP, The Armored March, and this new EP will serve as a bookend behind the three full-length albums. \"We have nothing against the traditional label model necessarily, we are just very excited by these new mediums,\" added Kinard. <span>Oh, Sleeper</span>','http://mickieszoo.blogspot.com/2013/04/oh-sleeper-seeks-funds-for-new-ep-and.html','2013-04-26T00:00:00','2013-04-26T17:12:59');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.summary,ENBlogs.url,ENBlogs.date_found,ENBlogs.date_posted) VALUES ('298c6122689c7847702ef0a2f0df3124','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','Oh, Sleeper Start Indiegogo For New EP','<span>Oh, Sleeper</span> has started an Indiegogo campaign to raise funds for its new EP Submitted by Niko John <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> Start Indiegogo For New EP','http://www.absolutepunk.net/showthread.php?t=3146051','2013-04-25T00:00:00','2013-04-25T17:53:34');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENBlogs (ENBlogs.blog_id,ENBlogs.artist_id,ENBlogs.name,ENBlogs.su