he-pitch-ex-periphery-vocalist-guests/','2013-06-22T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('6ae0ba3e90977604f63b4019206c088e','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','Oh, Sleeper Pushing Forward With Two New Crowdfunded EP\'s','Having officially exceeded their crowdfunding goal by $24,000, <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> will now be working on two new EP\'s. They issued the following update on their plans: \"We have been at breakneck speed since the triumphant end of the campaign and just want to say THANK YOU for your tremendous support! Because of this amazing support we are extremely proud to announce that we WILL be reserving enough funds raised over our goal to schedule time after Warped Tour to hit the studio to make a SECOND EP! We aren\'t sure of the date because it will have to fit in when our touring schedule permits, but we will definitely ... response. We will release a single, \"THE PITCH,\" ASAP. We are getting all of the merchandise and everything else into production for all of the awesome funders. We\'ve never been in charge of doing ALL of this before haha, but it\'s an exciting challenge. Look for more updates! Due to the insane rush that we\'ve been experiencing in this time crunch, we haven\'t had a lot of time to make updates about the process, but we thank you so much for your patience. Stay tuned, The Titan EP is coming soon! And of course TITAN will be available to everyone soon!\" <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> Pushing Forward With Two New Crowdfunded EP\'s','http://www.theprp.com/2013/06/15/news/oh-sleeper-pushing-foward-with-two-new-crowdfunded-eps/','2013-06-15T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('cddd3232e23fb1492f46bb8563d4a6c1','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','Oh, Sleeper Officially Surpass Their Crowdfunding Goal For New EP And Touring Costs','<span>Oh, Sleeper</span> have officially surpassed their crowdfunding goal of $30,000 USD for their new EP and touring vehicle expenses. As of this posting the band have raised $34,068 USD with eight days left to go on the campaign. As a result of the funding, the band expect to have a new EP out this summer, likely during their stint on this years \'Vans Warped Tour\'. <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> Officially Surpass Their Crowdfunding Goal For New EP And Touring Costs','http://www.theprp.com/2013/05/17/news/oh-sleeper-officially-surpass-their-crowdfunding-goal-for-new-ep-and-touring-costs/','2013-05-17T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('eb967a0217b7df67941e4823b1db09d2','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','Oh, Sleeper Launch IndieGoGo Campaign To Fund New EP','Former Solid State Records metal band <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> is on their own now and are asking fans for help in releasing their next batch of songs. They\'ve started an IndieGoGo campaign to raise $30,000 for the production of the EP and to repair their van and trailer for traveling. Check out the details below... <span>OH, SLEEPER</span> will record and release a brand new EP this summer while getting some much needed repairs to their van and trailer in order to stay on the road! OH SLEEPER is sponsored by The Artery Foundation; a worldwide, full service artist management company committed to every aspect of our band\'s careers.We\'ve given so much of our lives to <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> and you guys have given so much back to us. All of the symbols, lyrics and other tattoos we\'ve seen, all of the singing along at shows, it\'s been an incredible journey across an EP and three albums. We\'ve toured to all kinds of exciting places and met so many of your excellent people, whether on the road with bands like Every Time I Die, Bring Me The Horizon, Devil Wears Prada, Emery or Falling In Reverse, you guys have always supported us. We want to give back. We have found ourselves finished with our album contract and after talking with our old label and several prospective new ones, we decided to hit the PAUSE button and started talking about doing this ourselves this time. And doing it WITH YOU. We need some repairs to our van, a new trailer, but moreover, we want to release a BRAND NEW EP OF <span>OH, SLEEPER</span> MUSIC based on an awesome concept from Micah and brand new music from the band this summer. We\'ll be out on Warped all summer and we want you all to be part of the experience. We have all the power right now and we want to share that power with YOU. We have set a funding goal of $30,000. Where will that go?  To record and release a brand new EP and get it to you ASAP!  To get ... the two EPs will of course equal a brand new full-length\'s worth of material. So what do you get for helping us, besides our neverending gratitude? Check out all of the perk packages! Even if you can\'t contribuite, if you can get the word out about this campaign, that would be rad! We are so excited to take this project on by ourselves and to rely on YOU GUYS, the ones who have always made things happen for us, 100%! The digital, physical and vinyl artwork will all be unique from each other! ### For more info on <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> visit the JFH Artists Database. <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> Launch IndieGoGo Campaign To Fund New EP','http://jesusfreakhideout.com/news/2013/04/29.Oh,%20Sleeper%20Launch%20IndieGoGo%20Campaign%20To%20Fund%20New%20EP.asp','2013-04-29T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('870d03686978ada933996c3e86a0a819','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','Oh, Sleeper Can On Fans For Help','<span>Oh, Sleeper</span> are turning to fans and asking for their help to fund a new EP from the band and also purchase a new trailer and repairing their touring van so they can continue touring. The band has launched a campaign at Indiegogo and has set a $30,000 goal. As of Friday morning, they had already raised just under $7,900 dollars. They plan to use the money for the trailer and van repairs but also to record a new EP with producer Andreas Magnusson and according to the announcement if they raise enough money they may be able record a second EP. \"We are so excited, anxious, nervous and stoked to venture out with ... passionate responses from our fans over the years, we are so excited to get even closer to them now.\" Guitarist/vocalist Shane Blay adds: \"We\'re going to be on Warped Tour all summer for the first time and we want all of our supporters to be part of the experience. Launching this EP and getting some road repairs done this way just felt perfect.\" You can find out more details and prizes for various levels of donations here. <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> Tour Dates/Tickets <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> CDs, DVDs and MP3s <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> T-shirts and Posters <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> CDs, vinyl and rarities . ...end .News Reports <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> Can On Fans For Help','http://www.antimusic.com/news/13/April/26Oh,_Sleeper_Can_On_Fans_For_Help.shtml','2013-04-26T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('05d518139cdab7a9c004d2e3f678d32a','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','Oh, Sleeper Hoping To Crowdfund New EP And Touring Vehicle Expenses','<span>Oh, Sleeper</span> have opted to go the crowdfunding route for a new concept EP, a new trailer and some van repairs. The group have launched this Indiegogo campaign to help raise their goal of $30,000 USD. If successful, they plan to once again enter the studio with producer Andreas Magnusson (The Black Dahlia Murder, Impending Doom) to track the EP. Band frontman Micah Kinard said of the campaign: \"We are so excited, anxious, nervous and stoked to venture out with something like this. We know there are a lot of great methods of making and delivering music these days. After talking to several labels and looking at all of the \'crowd-funding\' options, we really felt like Indiegogo was the right place to make our next move. We have gotten such passionate responses from our fans over the years, we are so excited to get even closer to them now.\" Seeing the band go the crowdfunding route is not a surprise given their guitarist Shane Blay\'s explanation of mid-level bands making no money from a few years back. This summer will find <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> on the road as part of the \'Vans Warped Tour\'. Meanwhile, the below video for the campaign was also posted. <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> Hoping To Crowdfund New EP And Touring Vehicle Expenses','http://www.theprp.com/2013/04/25/news/oh-sleeper-hoping-to-crowdfund-new-ep-and-touring-vehicle-expenses/','2013-04-25T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,ENNews.summary,ENNews.url,ENNews.date_found) VALUES ('ad4703086bb78a3d928e11118a36059d','ARDBRC81187FB49B20','Vans Warped Tour Announces 2013 Dates and Lineup Including Motion City Soundtrack, Chiodos, Sleeping with the Sirens and More','Stephan Jacobs Kairo Kingdom Gabe Kubanda letlive. Like Moths To Flames Lionz of Zion Lost In Atlantis Mac Lethal Madchild Man Overboard MC Lars Memphis May Fire Middle Finger Salute Mixtapes Mighty Mongo Motion City Soundtrack Never Shout Never New Beat Fund New Empire New Years Day No Bragging Rights <span>Oh, Sleeper</span> Outasight Pacific Dub Psycho White RDGLDGRN Real Friends Reel Big Fish Relient K Run DMT Secrets Set It Off The Sheds Shy KidX. Silverstein Sleeping With Sirens Stick To Your Guns Story of the Year The Story So Far Strawberry Blondes The Summer Set Super Water Sympathy The Swellers Texas','http://www.mxdwn.com/2013/04/03/news/vans-warped-tour-announces-2013-dates-and-lineup-including-motion-city-soundtrack-chiodos-sleeping-with-the-sirens-and-more/','2013-04-03T00:00:00');INSERT IGNORE INTO ENNews (ENNews.news_id,ENNews.artist_id,ENNews.name,